Slain university student Sharon Otieno will be buried on October 19, her family announced yesterday. Ms Otieno was killed after she was kidnapped on September 3. Yesterday, Sharon's mother Melida Auma said their daughter would be buried at her grandfather's compound, next to her homestead. ALSO READ:

